3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The proposed algorithm is a distributed resource allocation algorithm, which can be considered as a control system. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper mentions maximizing the weighted sum of user rates, which can be related to multimedia applications.
